title: Had no intention of physically harming Kejriwal: Delhi BJP’s Tajinder Bagga on FIR against him - The Indian Express
content: Had no intention of physically harming Kejriwal: Delhi BJP’s Tajinder Bagga on FIR against him  The Indian ExpressView Full coverage on Google News
description: On Saturday, the Punjab and Haryana High Court granted Tajinder Bagga protection from any coercive action till the next date of hearing.
